back\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Feb 25, 2026</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104gpe1701568251563.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gpe1701568251563.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gpe1701568251563.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"gpe1701568251563\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Validates the widget.</p>\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">validate()</code></p>\n<p class=\"p\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Arguments</strong></p>\n<p class=\"p\">None</p>\n<p class=\"p\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Exceptions</strong></p>\n<p class=\"p\">None</p>\n<p class=\"p\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Return value</strong></p>\n<p class=\"p\">An error message (string), null, or undefined.</p>\n<p class=\"p\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Description</strong></p>\n<p class=\"p\">The framework calls the <code class=\"ph codeph\">validate()</code> function during the validation\n\t\t\tprocess to give the widget an opportunity to do widget validation before the framework\n\t\t\tperforms the Uniface validation. If the <code class=\"ph codeph\">validate()</code> function returns a\n\t\t\tnon-empty string, the framework will assume that the widget contains an error. The error\n\t\t\toccurred is used as string for the error message. If the <code class=\"ph codeph\">validate()</code>\n\t\t\tfunction returns nothing, or an empty string, the framework will perform the Uniface\n\t\t\tvalidation.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"gpe1701568251563__note_bs5_5kk_mhc\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span>\n<p class=\"p\">This API function is only fired for field-level widgets.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5442897\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5442897\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "validate Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Feb 25, 2026 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Validates the widget. validate() Arguments None Exceptions None Return value An error message (string), null, or undefined. Description The framework calls the validate() function during the validation process to give the widget an opportunity to do widget validation before the framework performs the Uniface validation. If the validate() function returns a non-empty string, the framework will assume that the widget contains an error. The error occurred is used as string for the error message. If the validate() function returns nothing, or an empty string, the framework will perform the Uniface validation. Note: This API function is only fired for field-level widgets. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}